summary: TL* THE CONTACT OWNS A 1967 CHEVROLET C-10 PICKUP TRUCK. THE CONTACT STATED THAT AFTER REPLACING THE FACTORY SEAT BELT WITH A DELUX SEAT BELT RETRACTOR, PART NUMBER: IN-432027, THE LOCKING MECHANISM SHATTERED AND SEPARATED WHILE CONNECTING THE SEAT BELT. THE CAUSE OF THE FAILURE WAS NOT YET DETERMINED. THE PARTS PLACE INC., LOCATED AT 630 ENTERPRISE AVENUE DEKALB, IL 60115 WAS NOTIFIED OF THE FAILURE.
